name: Portrait of Pembroke Welsh Corgi Named Dumbo
description:
Dumbo just turned 1 year old November 2021.

He is very smart, understand commands from us such as, sit, stay, hand, up, and etc.

Dumbo likes to people rub his belly.

Everytime I meet Dumbo, he always asked me to rub his belly.

He will come to me, he will give his head first to my hand, and then he lay to me.

And then he will enjoy his belly being rubbed by me.

I am looking forward to make Dumbo famous.

Let's make him a celebdog!
